WAIT! - Don't go pasting this on your site willy nilly.

You need to visit www.pubnub.com to get your API Key
so you can make real time cross domain JSON connections.

    To add on your website, go here:
    http://www.pubnub.com/app-showcase/traffic-beat

Otherwise Here is a description:

Traffic Beat is a view into live human traffic on your website.
Keep your web browser open and watch real humans visit as the
numbers tick up and down.

Traffic Beat does not show web crawlers and bots, only real people.
There are several customizations including full CSS Style control.
Traffic Beat is compatible with all web browsers and mobile devices.
Click the button above or this link to Add Traffic Beat on your website.
